  "detailed_description": "Cause reactions, discover new elements, and gain gold for your efforts in Elements For Money!<br><br>Every turn, you can move your elements around and get a new one from the shop. Adjacent elements can react to form new elements or provide gold bonuses for being next to other elements.<br><br>Get enough gold before payment to stay in the game, and obtain a high total gold count to get as high of a rank as you can.<br><strong><br>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>90+ elements to discover!<br></li><li>~1000 reactions to cause!<br></li><li>Playable with mouse and/or keyboard (support for both)!<br></li><li>A randomized shop for roguelike gameplay!<br></li><li>A variety of strategies to get high profit!<br></li><li>Gold to gain!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766500/extras/8836df64859a5bcde2bafadb0d8e05e8.poster.avif?t=1706205612\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766500/extras/8836df64859a5bcde2bafadb0d8e05e8.webm?t=1706205612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766500/extras/8836df64859a5bcde2bafadb0d8e05e8.mp4?t=1706205612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Cause reactions, discover new elements, and gain gold for your efforts in Elements For Money!<br><br>Every turn, you can move your elements around and get a new one from the shop. Adjacent elements can react to form new elements or provide gold bonuses for being next to other elements.<br><br>Get enough gold before payment to stay in the game, and obtain a high total gold count to get as high of a rank as you can.<br><strong><br>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>90+ elements to discover!<br></li><li>~1000 reactions to cause!<br></li><li>Playable with mouse and/or keyboard (support for both)!<br></li><li>A randomized shop for roguelike gameplay!<br></li><li>A variety of strategies to get high profit!<br></li><li>Gold to gain!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766500/extras/8836df64859a5bcde2bafadb0d8e05e8.poster.avif?t=1706205612\" width=640 height=186 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766500/extras/8836df64859a5bcde2bafadb0d8e05e8.webm?t=1706205612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2766500/extras/8836df64859a5bcde2bafadb0d8e05e8.mp4?t=1706205612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
